title.rendered: List of Qualified Applicants for Community Midwifery and their Exam Venues

content.rendered:
The under-listed applicants are qualified to write the Entrance Examination into COMMUNITY Midwifery Programme scheduled for Wednesday 3rd February, 2021. They should come along with their Acknowledgement Cards and Letter of Identification of Residence to their Exam Venues. They should check their names and Classrooms/Halls where they will sit for their exams. No applicants will be allowed to sit for the exams where he/she is not assigned to.
